{"tid":2188164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：楊明撞冧古牆 區會一致通過追數（李八方）","createTime":"2020-09-04T05:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T06:17:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd79d13e65f145ae9876434233f3f6dfdea7338","tid":2188164,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/U6H2WAO4QRAWXI3JOMGD6XRRLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FU6H2WAO4QRAWXI3JOMGD6XRRLM%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cUBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=7c1e5683\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FU6H2WAO4QRAWXI3JOMGD6XRRLM%2F&h=bd414bf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/U6H2WAO4QRAWXI3JOMGD6XRRLM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：楊明撞冧古牆 區會一致通過追數（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oIOaHl7rty6b_dGAz6mw40vitsk=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5J7RTKEQKVFH5G3ZQXFJSN4INQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoIOaHl7rty6b_dGAz6mw40vitsk%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5J7RTKEQKVFH5G3ZQXFJSN4INQ.jpg&h=97e1d02e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被撞毀嘅石牆有超過80年歷史，中西區區議會要求「原汁原味」重建。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n話說撐警藝人楊明上月初涉醉酒駕駛撞毀一段超過80年歷史嘅三米砌石牆，曾經有人估計楊明要賠成25萬維修費，但實際上政府點樣追數呢，噚日中西區區議會就搵政府部門同大家交代下。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n點解八方話政府似乎唔多着緊？因為中西區區議會要求咗五個政府部門出席會議，包括古物古蹟辦事處、路政署、警務處等，原本個個都回覆話唔去，最後只得路政署派咗人去，其他部門影都無。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/egN-Z75lUnUmmzs9NDY7S9WL2Dc=/886x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4T7IGYWABJFGDPAVG65VM6D7O4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FegN-Z75lUnUmmzs9NDY7S9WL2Dc%3D%2F886x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4T7IGYWABJFGDPAVG65VM6D7O4.jpg&h=ca4bd574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■撐警藝人楊明（中）曾「中伏」，同黃店員工合照。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甘乃威要求原汁原味重建<br />\n<br />\n路政署話石牆嘅修復工程喺8月27日已完成，仲話已經保留咗大部份原本嘅石塊，但民主黨甘乃威話路政署做呢類工程一向揦西，要求「原汁原味」重建，亦有議員關心維修費用，同埋邊個畀錢。路政署又話按既定機制，估算完維修費用後就會向涉事司機發信，詢問會唔會繳交款項，如果事主唔肯畀就會再向警方查詢睇法，然後問法律部門下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n路政署講完大堆嘢，即係原則上要楊明畀維修費，但收唔收到又另一回事！但中西區區議會就唔理咁多，一致通過動議要求路政署用「原汁原味」重砌石牆，同埋並依法向楊明追討維修費。"},{"pid":"20ff9c692550129fa91799af1715bcd0084fe827","tid":2188164,"uid":335434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"//路政署又話按既定機制，估算完維修費用後就會向涉事司機發信，詢問會唔會繳交款項，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">如果事主唔肯畀就會再向警方查詢睇法</span></strong></span>，然後問法律部門下一步行動。//<br />\n<br />\n結果己經呼之欲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6196d583585e784c1d4d0e1a3c783d3d77afc0","tid":2188164,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1351bf04f149a7eb7d8d6cf4a111a164e118d9d","tid":2188164,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660f80197dea3b91a3505ef839b337e6ed79bdf1","tid":2188164,"uid":301503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6344f5e3beddaee472558b84b972019a869669c0","tid":2188164,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:38:40.000Z","msg":"最後九成唔駛賠"},{"pid":"14495ad3d55040b1f17e6c34f195481